* 韩国和美国于2月27日取消了原计划在2020年3月举行的联合军演。<ref>{{cite web|title=U.S., South Korea Cancel Military Exercises Amid Coronavirus Spike|url=https://www.usnews.com/news/world-report/articles/2020-02-27/us-south-korea-cancel-military-exercises-amid-coronavirus-spike|date=2020-02-27|last=Shinkman|first=Paul D.|website=[[U.S._News_&_World_Report|U.S. News & World Report]]|accessdate=2020-08-30|archive-date=2020-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411014645/https://www.usnews.com/news/world-report/articles/2020-02-27/us-south-korea-cancel-military-exercises-amid-coronavirus-spike|dead-url=no}}</ref>
