== 海军舰艇 ==
{{main| 2019冠状病毒病海军舰艇疫情}}

2019冠状病毒病疫情蔓延到许多海军舰船，这种舰船本身的工作性质就是人们会在狭小封闭的区域与其他人一起工作，并且绝大多数官兵缺乏个人住所或者床鋪密集，这导致了病毒的快速传播，情况甚至比邮轮上还严重，其中美國船艦有11艘。<ref>{{cite web|title=After Discovering a Sailor With Coronavirus, the U.S. Navy Crowded Dozens Into One Room|url=https://www.propublica.org/article/after-discovering-a-sailor-with-coronavirus-the-us-navy-crowded-dozens-into-one-room|date=16 March 2020|last=Faturechi|first=Robert|work=Propublica.org|last2=Rose|first2=Megan|last3=Miller|first3=T. Christan|last-author-amp=y|access-date=8 April 2020|archive-date=2020-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515171646/https://www.propublica.org/article/after-discovering-a-sailor-with-coronavirus-the-us-navy-crowded-dozens-into-one-room|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Exclusive: Captain of aircraft carrier with growing coronavirus outbreak pleads for help from Navy|url=https://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/article/Exclusive-Captain-of-aircraft-carrier-with-15167883.php|date=31 March 2020|last=Gafni|first=Matthias|work=San Francisco Chronicle|last2=Garofoli|first2=Joe|last-author-amp=y|access-date=8 April 2020|archive-date=2020-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519124659/https://www.sfchronicle.com/bayarea/article/Exclusive-Captain-of-aircraft-carrier-with-15167883.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

